ping Galilean satellite\nelemental composition) in-situ X-ray instrumentation is a necessity. Recent\nadvances enable compact, lightweight, X-ray instrumentation perfectly suited\nfor Jupiter science. The chapter closes by reviewing feasible, low-risk\nconcepts that would paradigm-shift our understanding of the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 09:48:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
