ced fun, hints had a positive effect. Generally, we found programming\nthe Ozobot Evo to be encouraging for both girls and boys. To support teachers,\nwe discuss ideas for giving encouraging feedback on common problems of Ozobot\nEvo programming activities and how our findings transfer to other robots.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 09:51:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
